## How to Delete a Chrome Profile

If you need to delete a Chrome account or profile for privacy reasons, follow these steps:

1. Open Chrome and click the profile icon in the top-right corner.
2. Select "Manage Your Google Account."
3. Choose the profile to delete and click "More Options."
4. Confirm the deletion.

![Delete Chrome profile](https://cdn-customer.helplook.net/_hl/load-img.DSGdRIBO.png)

**Note**: Deleting a profile will erase all associated browsing data, including bookmarks, history, and passwords.

